The paper presents a new method for adapting proposal distributions in Sequential Monte Carlo (SMC) using neural networks, which is a topic related to machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The method is applied to state space models and recurrent neural networks, which are topics related to control systems (cs.SY), statistics (cs.ST), and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.LG and cs.AI, followed by cs.SY, cs.ST, and cs.NE.
